nm:output.nm:control_stream:
$PROBLEM 10 mixture model and IOV on CL $INPUT C ID DV AMT II ADDL TIME RATE HT WT CLCR SEX AGE EVID VIST MDV $DATA ../MixSim.csv IGNORE=C $SUB ADVAN1 TRANS2 $MIX NSPOP=2 P(1)=THETA(6) P(2)=1.-THETA(6) $PK ;IOV VST1=0 IF(VIST.EQ.1) VST1=1 VST2=0 IF(VIST.EQ.2) VST2=1 VST3=0 IF(VIST.EQ.3) VST3=1 EST=MIXEST IF (MIXNUM.EQ.1) THEN TVCL=THETA(1)*(WT/70)**THETA(3) ELSE TVCL=THETA(5)*(WT/70)**THETA(3) ENDIF
CL=TVCL*EXP(ETA(1) + ETA(3)*VST1 + ETA(4)*VST2 + ETA(5)*VST3) TVV=THETA(2)*(WT/70)**THETA(4) V=TVV*EXP(ETA(2)) S1=V $ERROR Y=F + F*ERR(1) + ERR(2) IPRED=F $THETA (0, 12) ;1. CL POP 1 (0, 150);2. V (0.75) ;3. WT ON CL (1) ;4. WT ON V (0, 1) ;5. CL POP 2 (0, 0.5, 1) ;6. PROB POP 1 $OMEGA (0.04) ;1. CL VAR (0.04) ;2. V VAR ;IOV $OMEGA BLOCK(1) 0.04; interoccasion var in CL $OMEGA BLOCK(1) SAME $OMEGA BLOCK(1) SAME $SIGMA 0.04 10 ;$MSFI=./2.msf $EST PRINT=5 MAX=9999 METHOD=1 POSTHOC NOABORT $COV
